of people on a waiting list,

00:09:18,531 --> 00:09:20,867
and as soon as Dee Zee gets
production ramped up,

00:09:20,867 --> 00:09:22,202
I believe
the sky's the limit.

00:09:22,202 --> 00:09:23,870
Well, Donny, that's
the first one off the line.

00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:25,405
What do you think?
Looks great.

00:09:25,405 --> 00:09:28,141
Even though I didn't get
a deal on "Shark tank,"

00:09:28,141 --> 00:09:29,642
it's pretty overwhelming to see

00:09:29,642 --> 00:09:30,777
the product that I invented
in my garage

00:09:30,777 --> 00:09:33,379
now in a manufacturing facility
being produced

00:09:33,379 --> 00:09:37,784
by lots of American workers.
It's--It's exciting.

